<!-- MISSION -->
<section class="about-section bg-subtle" style="text-align:center;">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label" style="justify-content:center;">🎯 Our Mission</p>
    <h2 style="margin:0 auto 20px;">Making opportunities accessible</h2>
    <p style="margin:0 auto 16px;font-size:1.15rem;">The goal is simple — make it easier for talented people to find fellowships, internships, accelerators, tech jobs, and important updates shaping the future of design and technology.</p>
    <p style="margin:0 auto;font-size:1.15rem;">Too many brilliant designers and developers across Africa and beyond never reach their full potential — not because of lack of talent, but because they simply don't know what's available to them. DesignTechNews exists to close that gap.</p>
  </div>
</section>

