    <div class="founder-inner">
        <div style="width:270px;height:405px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;flex-shrink:0;">                    <img src="/images/founder.png" alt="Lebari Pado" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" />
        </div>     
        <div class="founder-content">
            <h2>Lebari Pado</h2>
        <p class="founder-title">
          <span>Founder & Curator, DesignTechNews</span>
        </p>
        <p>DesignTechNews was born out of personal frustration. Early in my career as a designer, I spent countless hours scattered across dozens of websites, social media feeds, and WhatsApp groups just trying to find opportunities that were relevant to me — scholarships I qualified for, jobs that matched my skills, fellowships that could open doors. The information existed, but it was fragmented, buried, and hard to trust.</p>
        <p>I built DesignTechNews to be the resource I wished I had — a single, reliable place where creatives across Africa and the world can find what they need without the noise. Every opportunity, job listing, and article is hand-picked with the community in mind.</p>
        <p>DesignTechNews is an independent project built and curated by a designer and tech enthusiast passionate about connecting creatives with opportunities that can genuinely change their lives.</p>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/lebari-pado" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="founder-linkedin">
